snippet: Two large bombings in Shiite-majority neighborhoods in Baghdad killed at least 18 people on Saturday.
abstract: Two large suicide bombings in Baghdad's Shiite neighborhoods kill at least 18 people and injure more than 61; there is no claim of responsibility, but similar bombings have been carried out by Islamic State.
